OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1775218269
OL,3,CHealth chiefs confirm suspected case
OL,4,Cof meningitis at North East school
OL,6,FIn a statement, headteacher Chris
OL,7,FColeman said: "We have been given
OL,8,Fassurances from the UK Health Security
OL,9,FAgency that the risk to our students
OL,10,Fremains low and they should continue
OL,11,Ftheir normal activities."
OL,13,FThe outbreak in Kent in recent weeks
OL,14,Fhas seen the loss of two young lives
OL,15,Fand a vaccination programme rolled out.
OL,17,FThe UK Health Security Agency has
OL,18,Fstressed that cases are expected to
OL,19,Fappear around the country.
OL,26,@sD@YO]
