PN,42503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1775218269
OL,3,CHealth chiefs confirm suspected case
OL,4,Cof meningitis at North East school
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the department
OL,7,Fsaid: "Every year in this country more
OL,8,Fthan 350 cases of meningococcal
OL,9,Finfection are reported ` that's
OL,10,Fequivalent to almost one a day.
OL,12,F"Therefore, we would expect to see
OL,13,Fother cases of meningococcal infection
OL,14,Faround the country, which are not
OL,15,Fconnected at all to the situation in
OL,16,FKent."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/4
